"{\"uid\": \"express.co.uk-sport-othersport-1965012-Imane-Khelif-Olympics-gender-row-boxing\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"  Imane Khelif, fresh off herOlympictriumph in Paris, confirmed that she planned to become a professional boxer just months after snatching a gold medal.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 153, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 14, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}, {\"begin\": 47, \"end\": 52, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999974434104, \"rank\": 2.556519241002095e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Algerian sensation faced a storm of controversy during her Olympic journey, having been previously barred from the World Championships by the International Boxing Association (IBA) following gender eligibility tests.\", \"from\": 155, \"to\": 375, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 159, \"end\": 167, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9971983433575031, \"rank\": 0.002614512373525501, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 301, \"end\": 333, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.888733563417979e-26, \"text\": \"International Boxing Association\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Women's_International_Boxing_Association\"}, {\"begin\": 335, \"end\": 338, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"score\": 0.9936205293020296, \"rank\": 0.006420313934579829, \"text\": \"IBA\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Independent_Broadcasting_Authority\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A matter for which, notably, no irrefutable evidence has been presented.\", \"from\": 376, \"to\": 448, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"At just 25, Khelif not only made history by securing Algeria's first female boxing gold with her resounding 5-0 victory over Yang Liu in the women's 66kg category but also became the centre of contention as the Games progressed.\", \"from\": 450, \"to\": 678, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 503, \"end\": 510, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9998656005438958, \"rank\": 0.00011278437733270486, \"text\": \"Algeria\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}, {\"begin\": 575, \"end\": 583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liu_Yang_(violinist)\", \"score\": 0.9999966834675861, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Yang Liu\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liu_Yang_(violinist)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Liu_Yang_(violinist)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Angela Carini dramatically withdrew from their bout after less than a minute, visibly distressed and foregoing the customary post-match handshake, though she later expressed regret over the ensuing controversy.\", \"from\": 680, \"to\": 890, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 680, \"end\": 693, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"score\": 0.9999962103660394, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Angela Carini\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Angela_Carini\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In August, an emotionally wounded Khelif disclosed the extent of the vitriol aimed in her direction, as rampant speculation about her gender marred the Olympics experience.\", \"from\": 892, \"to\": 1064, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"After her triumph in Paris, the Algerian now has set her sights on a new challenge in the ring - turning pro.\", \"from\": 1066, \"to\": 1175, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1087, \"end\": 1092, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999974434104, \"rank\": 2.556519241002095e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 1098, \"end\": 1106, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"score\": 0.9971983433575031, \"rank\": 0.002614512373525501, \"text\": \"Algerian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Algeria\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Addressing the media on Sunday, she declared: \\\"I would like to hold a press conference today to share with you my success story with the media family and young women who watch me.\", \"from\": 1176, \"to\": 1355, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"There is a documentary being prepared about my success story and it will be shown on international platforms.\", \"from\": 1357, \"to\": 1467, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I will soon enter the world of professional boxing, I have many offers.\", \"from\": 1468, \"to\": 1539, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Currently, I have not made up my mind about where I will enter professional boxing.\", \"from\": 1540, \"to\": 1623, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"But very soon I will take this step, we as Algerians would like to see our level in the field of professionalism.\\\"\", \"from\": 1624, \"to\": 1738, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Earlier in the month, there was a flurry of false reports that Khelif had been stripped of her Olympic glory, which triggered theWorld Boxing Organisation to clarify the situation firmly.\", \"from\": 1740, \"to\": 1927, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1875, \"end\": 1881, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\", \"score\": 0.9999999995739017, \"rank\": 4.25900559957202e-10, \"text\": \"Boxing\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Boxing\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Online speculation suggested that the 25-year-old had been disqualified and faced a lifetime ban from the WBO.\", \"from\": 1928, \"to\": 2038, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"However, given her amateur status, such sanctions would fall well outside the governing body's remit.\", \"from\": 2042, \"to\": 2143, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The World Boxing Organisation has informed that it had not tested, nor has it banned female boxer Imane Khelif, who won a gold medal during the boxing tournament of the 2024 Olympics in Paris, France,\\\" their official statement confirmed.\", \"from\": 2145, \"to\": 2383, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2150, \"end\": 2175, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Boxing_Organization\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"World Boxing Organisation\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Boxing_Organization\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Boxing_Organization\"}, {\"begin\": 2244, \"end\": 2256, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"score\": 0.9999996421621021, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Imane Khelif\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Imane_Khelif\"}, {\"begin\": 2332, \"end\": 2337, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999974434104, \"rank\": 2.556519241002095e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 2339, \"end\": 2345, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9043998747548421, \"rank\": 0.08706537622885684, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2385, \"to\": 2494, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2495, \"to\": 2571, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2572, \"to\": 2604, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  WBO legal counsel Gustavo Olivieri, Esq.\", \"from\": 2605, \"to\": 2669, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2647, \"end\": 2654, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gustavo_A._Madero\", \"score\": 0.9978152567794212, \"rank\": 0.0021894272573920294, \"text\": \"Gustavo\", \"types\": [\"Q82955\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gustavo_A._Madero\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Gustavo_A._Madero\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"clarified: \\\"The report claiming that the WBO had banned Khelif are obviously false.\", \"from\": 2670, \"to\": 2753, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2711, \"end\": 2714, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Boxing_Organization\", \"score\": 0.999750911524918, \"rank\": 0.0002491505358040685, \"text\": \"WBO\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Boxing_Organization\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Boxing_Organization\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We have had no communication with Khelif.\", \"from\": 2754, \"to\": 2795, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We congratulate her and wish her luck in all her future endeavours.\\\"\", \"from\": 2796, \"to\": 2864, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He further emphasised: \\\"Any report stating otherwise is obviously fake and ill-intentioned.\\\"\", \"from\": 2866, \"to\": 2958, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 2960, \"to\": 3129, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3097, \"end\": 3110, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.933890737956014e-18, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 3131, \"to\": 3198, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3146, \"end\": 3159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.933890737956014e-18, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}]}"